        "subject": "LU-4336 quota: improper assert in osc_quota_chkdq()",
        "message": "LU-4336 quota: improper assert in osc_quota_chkdq()\n\nIn osc_quota_chkdq(), we should never try to access oqi found\nfrom hash, since it could have been freed by osc_quota_setdq().\n\nBackport from: d21e835b9cacf14d92f61a99b8514e28e98fb4a0\n\nSigned-off-by: Niu Yawei <yawei.niu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I6a1d5672605501a21507aa49657366286c762f2e\n"
